{
  "stem": "23410.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and the only time when we had a Seder with other family members was in my case never, because my father never left the family for Pesach or for high holidays to the Rebbe, to the Belzer Rebbe.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there were families where the men left to be with the Rebbe.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the families stayed at home behind.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they were invited with other parts of the family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But normally, not too much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because like my uncle that went to the Rebbe, and his wife and daughter spent the Pesach with his-- with her father and mother.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So it wasn't to go to the brother, or to the family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And everybody had a big family, like we had, [INAUDIBLE] example, we were seven children, and two grown-ups, and a helper-- a cleaning woman.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was 10 people in the house to start.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So it was, by itself, a Passover Seder, a Passover-- or any holiday, like [INAUDIBLE], a big table.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It wasn't that you invited people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The only people that you invited, if it happened-- it normal did not happen on holidays.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It happened on Shabbat-- was a poor man to come to dinner for Friday night.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "After the synagogue, you took him to dinner to your house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But otherwise, it was never a case that you had people or friends over for the holidays.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because they had their own holidays.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I came in at a time-- when I was a child, what I had, it was after the fight between two groups if machine matzos are Kosher or non-Kosher.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we started already with machine matzos.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we baked also matzos in every town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was you baked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You were a part of baking of the matzos.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And even the children went to bake matzos.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
